methods.param: (leafOnly, includeHalfChecked) Accept two boolean type parameters: 1. default value is false. If the parameter is true, it only returns the currently selected array of sub-nodes. 2. default value is false. If the parameter is true, the return value contains halfchecked nodes

methods.param: (keys, leafOnly) Accept two parameters: 1. an array of nodes keys to be checked 2. a boolean parameter. If set to true, only the checked status of leaf nodes will be set. The default value is false.

methods.param: (key/data, checked, deep) Accept three parameters: 1. nodes key or data to be checked 2. a boolean typed parameter indicating checked or not. 3. a boolean typed parameter indicating deep or not.
